OL,7,FIt's being claimed that the sculpture,
OL,8,Fwhich would cost #11 million pounds to
OL,9,Fbuild, could bring half a million
OL,10,Ftourists to the area annually and
OL,11,Fgenerate millions of pounds for the
OL,12,Flocal economy every year.
OL,14,FThe Caledonia Star Trust say they've
OL,15,Freceived offers of funding from a
OL,16,Fnumber of sources, including Community
OL,17,FWindpower, one of largest green energy
OL,18,Foperators, as well as from South of
OL,19,FScotland Enterprise and the
OL,20,FBorderlands Inclusive Growth Deal.
