OL,7,FThe structure would sit at thirty-five
OL,8,Fmetres tall and be illuminated at
OL,9,Fnight. In a statement the trust said
OL,10,Fit would "be clearly visible from the
OL,11,FM74 and form a stunning welcome and
OL,12,Ffarewell to Scotland for travellers."
OL,14,FAlongside the sculpture the trust
OL,15,Fwants to build a visitors centre which
OL,16,Fit says would highlight local
OL,17,Fattractions, including the Robert
OL,18,FBurns House in Dumfries and the Dark
OL,19,FSpace Planetarium Kirkcudbright, as
OL,20,Fwell as Hadrian's Wall.
